e with a bold 3-4 pixel solid black outline, positioned over `domina`'s side of the frame so the tail attribution is unambiguous; short triangular black-outlined tail pointing directly to `domina`'s mouth. bold black sans-serif comic display font ALL CAPS text inside (Bangers-style lettering, no shading, no extrusion) reads exactly: \"Yes, but there are other factors. For instance you said you found the meteorite... what if someone else, someone bad, finds another just like it?\". Flat 2D vector graphic \u2014 NO 3D shading, NO bevel/extrusion, NO translucency, NO chrome, NO drop shadow onto the scene. The lettering layer is composited ON TOP of the photoreal CGI render \u2014 like a comic letterer added bubbles and captions directly onto a photograph. The bodies and scene stay photoreal CGI; only the bubble / caption / SFX graphics are flat 2D overlay.\n\n[CLOSING ANCHOR \u2014 CGI scope]\nPhotographic CGI render on the bodies, costumes, skin, hair, environment, and lighting; NOT a 2D illustration on the bodies, NOT cartoon-shaded skin. Only the bubble / caption / SFX graphics are flat 2D comic-book overlay.",
